<h2 id="light-alarm">Light alarm</h2>

<p>In order to get the feeling of a sunrise when I have to wake up I created the following automation. About \(15\) minutes before my alarm clock gets of the light in my bedroom slowly aluminates until itâ€™s at full brightness.
I use a <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">input_datetime</code> so Iâ€™m able to easily change the wakeup time.</p>

<div class="language-yaml highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="na">input_datetime</span><span class="pi">:</span>
<span class="na">wakeup_time_lukas</span><span class="pi">:</span>
<span class="na">name</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="s1">'</span><span class="s">Wecken</span><span class="nv"> </span><span class="s">um'</span>
